Symptoms were yesterday, I really think I was already getting a cold before I got the shot. I already had gotten a fever blister the night before and waiting in line in the cold and wind probable  did me in.  To me the illness seem all standard cold related.  Today I am on a slow recovery for the normal cold, sleep a lot and liquids.  Once again I don't think it was vaccine shot related.
